dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data represents roads for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2019.[This data represents the centerlines of all roads in Calumet County. The data is used in nearly all aspects of the Land Information Office and is updated almost every day. Updates are performed using source documents (surveys, plats, etc) along with any available aerial imagery.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This data is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[This data represents the centerlines of all roads in Calumet County. The data was created by Calumet County and is continuously updated by the County.]
